{"tid":1335701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思-求士氣圖","createTime":"2019-07-20T15:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T16:26:13.000Z","uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"610fd829884479ecf06192cb623ba372bc128ca5","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人好似我心情<br />\n心情平伏，完全想像唔到聽日場仗點<br />\n有同伴突破唔到心理關口，戰意磨滅<br />\n場仗會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭理由唔止初初撤回逃犯條例要求<br />\n我們所有訴求當中有一個更大含意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要政府知道香港吾係隨便比你操控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 中共/政府：<br />\n咁多市民反抗都輸，更明目張膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 警察： <br />\n變回回歸前情況，貪污/濫用權力，想點就點。<br />\n對住警察唔再係對等，要好似面對老闆，另一個職場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 市民心態：<br />\n今次抗爭都失敗，之後再反抗都冇用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 香港：<br />\n全港享有大灣區機遇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 外國：<br />\n香港以後不用著重，香港人咁易忘記/放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要我們點幫你？浪費時間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 藍/紅底：<br />\n更加認為自己冇錯，正義勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想收集提高士氣信息（最好係圖）<br />\n聽日資料圖就唔好留一堆，一張就夠「7/21」<br />\n動物台熱血gif、愛國青年參加64前gif，咩都好。<br />\n等同伴可以充充電，繼續發力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申番，小弟冇辦法出吾到黎助陣（勇武派），唯有做文宣。<br />\n絕對吾係玩、旅行、返工、懶、怕事"},{"pid":"a6f0477b919678ee37460089ecfe7c0fa0379944","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"唔好沉底，有一個士氣post出現會更好"},{"pid":"158e925a82bcc88d15a60821e6e1658ca5809764","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"2576926d1a3d1edf6603014b45845ebc0f189a61","tid":1335701,"uid":12171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/e0nvNFW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0nvNFW.gif&h=32930245&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eddc6813543fc4000e00a4b016b3622f356ca3d5","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"推呀，好需要士氣post，振奮人心"},{"pid":"e44bfece736efd8eafabc4cb41cf298daa26497e","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"咁多post都比人無視<br />\n唯獨呢個唔好呀"},{"pid":"d84ac5a934aabcea560ce7322db5e74f5e5c58c4","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7473302092a978836b1d730f81cd146653bf0d40","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80ecf491976a8d308c1e7a7b7bf031fcf4fb8c5f","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iI0umujg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiI0umujg.jpg&h=285a4ec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5a02e29d7f6e605c3439b6ecdffb02680fa5aac","tid":1335701,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KA5JNnG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKA5JNnG.png&h=c95e9e5a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}